name: version 1.8.0
body:
ScalikeJDBC 1.8.0 is out.  ScalikeJDBC 1.8.x doesn't support Scala 2.9. The reason is backporting Scala 2.9 incompatible changes from ScalikeJDBC 2.0.

Don't worry. We'll keep maintaining ScalikeJDBC 1.7.x for Scala 2.9 users.
- #254 backport
- Supports only Scala 2.10.x
- Still works with ScalaTest 1.9.x
